got old that quickly?

320
00:14:13,727 --> 00:14:16,772
I mean, monkeys in go-karts
was fun for a while.

321
00:14:16,855 --> 00:14:18,023
Then I was like,

322
00:14:18,107 --> 00:14:20,818
"You know what would be cool?
Hippos in go-karts!"

323
00:14:20,901 --> 00:14:24,613
