and made me captain.

341
00:15:12,536 --> 00:15:13,913
Well, I'm not giving up.

342
00:15:14,997 --> 00:15:17,917
We worked too hard
and went through too much.

343
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,710
I'm not gonna just sit back

344
00:15:19,793 --> 00:15:23,380
and turn into some slack-jawed,
sweatpant-wearing orgasm machine!

345
00:15:23,464 --> 00:15:24,340
Oh, my God!

346
00:15:24,423 --> 00:15:26,300
I'm describing
my dream existence like it's bad.

347
00:15:26,383 --> 00:15:28,177
What is wrong with this place?

348
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:29,929
We just redesigned this system,

349
00:15:30,012 --> 00:15:32,556
and soon millions of people
are going to start pouring in,

350
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:35,726
