370
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:40,958
Seems to me you can do whatever you want.

371
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:44,461
[Eleanor] Where is Michael?

372
00:16:46,505 --> 00:16:48,298
[chuckles] Okay.

373
00:16:48,382 --> 00:16:49,675
[laughs]

374
00:16:50,676 --> 00:16:53,512
Nothing to do but announce the big change.

375
00:16:53,595 --> 00:16:58,434
Whatever happens, it's cool, my babies.
It's very cool.

376
00:17:01,103 --> 00:17:02,521
Did you smoke that weed, bud?

377
00:17:02,604 --> 00:17:04,565
