379
00:17:06,442 --> 00:17:09,695
I was kinda freaked out,
so I smoked some grass, but now I'm great.

380
00:17:09,778 --> 00:17:12,865
Let's change the afterlife, and then...

381
00:17:12,948 --> 00:17:14,366
-Taco Bell.
-[Eleanor exclaims]

382
00:17:14,950 --> 00:17:18,162
Oh, baby!

383
00:17:18,245 --> 00:17:19,788
Okay, I'm gonna do the talking.

384
00:17:20,748 --> 00:17:23,125
[clears throat] Hi, everyone.
Can I have your attention, please?

385
00:17:23,208 --> 00:17:25,627
Hi, my name's Eleanor Shellstrop.

386
