414
00:19:11,608 --> 00:19:12,985
That's my boyfriend.

415
00:19:14,403 --> 00:19:16,321
I'm glad we'll be able to
enjoy things again.

416
00:19:16,405 --> 00:19:19,491
-Art, math, philosophy, like you used to.
-Yeah, me, too.

417
00:19:19,575 --> 00:19:25,247
