I think I'll stick around for a while.

419
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:33,088
It felt good to make brain words.

420
00:19:33,172 --> 00:19:35,966
Still mushy. I'll get it back.

421
00:19:36,049 --> 00:19:37,885
We're lucky we ran into you.

422
00:19:37,968 --> 00:19:38,969
It saved us.

423
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:42,181
