424
00:19:43,765 --> 00:19:45,642
-Hey!
-[Jason] Hey!

425
00:19:46,810 --> 00:19:48,645
-It was your friendships.
-Yeah, no, I got it.

426
00:19:49,229 --> 00:19:51,690
