428
00:19:57,696 --> 00:20:00,490
Even made myself an office nearby.

429
00:20:01,658 --> 00:20:06,079
Jason, I... I kinda took a wild guess...

430
00:20:07,164 --> 00:20:10,959
[Jason] I finally get to accomplish
my goal of living in a Stupid Nick's!

431
00:20:11,043 --> 00:20:12,961
I know anything you do
for eternity gets boring,

432
00:20:13,045 --> 00:20:15,631
{\an8}but I swear,
I will never get sick of wings.

433
00:20:16,673 --> 00:20:19,092
{\an8}Well, I'll see you all tomorrow.

434
00:20:19,968 --> 00:20:21,678
{\an8}And every tomorrow after that.

435
00:20:21,762 --> 00:20:24,765
{\an8}You know, Michael, at the end of the day,
you were right.

436
00:20:26,892 --> 00:20:28,894
{\an8}Everything is fine.

437
00:20:41,615 --> 00:20:42,532
{\an8}[chuckles softly]

438
00:20:46,870 --> 00:20:52,209
[Chidi] This is what we've been
looking for since the day we met... time.

439
00:20:52,292 --> 00:20:55,545
I guess that's what
the Good Place really is.

440
00:20:55,629 --> 00:20:56,713
It's not even a "place," really.

441
00:20:56,797 --> 00:21:01,760
It's just having enough time
with the people you love.

442
00:21:01,843 --> 00:21:02,886
You're right.

443
00:21:04,388 --> 00:21:06,807
And we have as long as we want.

444
00:21:09,685 --> 00:21:10,769
If you keep hogging this blanket,

445
00:21:10,852 --> 00:21:13,480
I'm probably gonna walk through that door
in three days, though.

446
00:21:15,065 --> 00:21:15,899
[chuckles]

447
00:21:18,110 --> 00:21:19,569
-[Chidi] I'll miss you.
-[Eleanor laughs]
